Hi everyone, hope everyone had a anger free
day yesterday. I did. Um anyway I went shopping

yesterday as you can see and look Jasmine
I have go the most stylish shoes in the world.

So much better then yours. Get that stinky
ugly shoe out of my face. Jasmine Barbie just

stop fighting all ready. Well anyway for steps
six of our program we are going to focus on

using humor in our anger. If you upset try
laughing at the situation instead of getting

angry. I will use the Beast as my example.
Beast hunny come here. Now Beast you have

dog breath your hair is shedding all over
the floor I am picking up clumps of hair all

the time. You never take out the garbage and
I think I am out of your league. What I take

out the garbage at least once a month. And
I have breath that smells like skittles okay.

And out of your league, I have many creatures
linning up to date me alright. Oh look when

he's angry his tail wags. Oh ha ha that is
pretty funny. I am not even angry anymore

that is just plane silly. I know its so cute.
Okay you can sit down now. As you could see

instead of getting super angry he found the
situation hilarious. Now let's see if you

can do this at home. Thanks for coming over
you two, I just need someone to talk to these

days besides Barbie. She is just crazy. Shes
going through anger management and shes doing

well okay but I just need to talk to someone
who is not nutso. Oh I am just glad I could

help you out Hans. As the Queen I really enjoy
helping people. And I do feel bad for you

in your situation because you know I have
been around Barbie too and she is not the

easiest to live with. I'm just here because
Elsa is here but of coarse I am also here

because I care so much about you guys and
I'm just so Spidy Spidy awesome, I'm here

to always help you know. Oh no shes here okay
be prepared guys you never know how shes going

to be. Oh hi, hi everyone oh hello Hansy-boo.
And Elsa I did't know you'd be here hugs,

your my bestie. Oh and hi Spidy, hope your
doing well. I just want to announce that I

am in such a good light hearted mood I just
returned from my day six class. Wow Barbie

you are in such a nice mood. WHat did you
learn about in class that put you in such

a happy mood? Oh it was a great session we
learned that we should take things more lightly.

And laugh off our anger so I am just going
to try and be in a happy mood and laugh alto.

And just not blow up in little things. So
if i told you, you really shouldn't have bought

that dress because it is a cheap fabric and
that shade of green does not look good on

you, you would juts laugh it off? And if i
told you that I really don't like all your

fake tanning and that the fake tanning has
gone a little too far you're looking like

an orange you wont be mad you'll just laugh
it off? And if I told you I accidentally shrunk

all of your jeans in the wash this morming
you wouldnt be mad either? You'll jus laugh

and think it's funny. Wait what? You don't
like my tan? And you don't like my dress?

and you shrunk my clothes? Ut's funny yea,
It's so funny. Alrighty then I am out of here.

Oh you guys are so funny. Oh you guys make
me laugh so much because your just so funny.

So much fun. Yea I don't think that whole
taking things funny so much is working out.

HA HA I'm just having so much fun laughing.
I have never felt better. Oh you guys think

I'm funny? Hilarious. I don't know if this
is exactly what therapy had in mind. Please

please I beg of you like this video and maybe
